title: Worlds Group Stage Day 2 MEGATHREAD
body:
SKT vs C9 it's gonna be interesting watching Impact against his former team. 

I think SKT is gonna wipe the floor with C9 but who knows, a lot of people thought TSM was gonna beat Royal ng but they did not. 

Hopefully TSM can bounce back but it's gonna be tough because samsung galaxy has their phones with no physical keyboards and no removable batteries .
